summary: This is a travel voucher notification email indicating final approval for expenses related to a trip for witness interviews in the U.S. v. Epstein case. The trip was to Santa Monica, CA from December 15-17, 2019, with a traveler named Minor.

persons.name: Minor

keyFacts: A travel voucher was approved for witness interviews in the U.S. v. Epstein case.
The traveler, named Minor, went to Santa Monica, CA from December 15-17, 2019.
The trip was associated with case reference R20NYS13257 - U.S. v. Epstein.
The voucher total expenses were $1,400.38 against an estimated trip cost of $1,907.95.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity in the Epstein case as of late 2019.
